data.description: This home is beautifully landscaped with a spacious back yard and a deck perfect for entertaining. The kitchen is open and airy, with ample counter space and storage. The master bath features a large walk-in shower and bright, clean countertops. The bonus room boasts natural light and space with the option for a fourth bedroom! Call today to schedule a private showing.
